<section class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-surface-container-lowest">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">

    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <span class="text-xs font-label uppercase tracking-widest text-primary font-semibold">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="font-headline font-bold text-4xl text-on-surface mt-3">Cancellation &amp; <span class="text-primary italic">Refund Policy</span></h1>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm mt-3">Last updated: April 2025</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-surface-container rounded-xl border border-surface-container-high p-8 space-y-8 text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">1. Overview</h2>
        <p>FullOnBaan offers digital training products including eBooks, video course bundles, and combo packages. Because these are digital goods that are delivered electronically, our cancellation and refund policy is as described below. We encourage you to review product descriptions carefully before purchasing.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">2. Order Cancellation</h2>
        <p>Once a payment is successfully processed and the digital product has been dispatched to your registered email address, the order cannot be cancelled. If you have not yet received your product and wish to cancel, please contact us within <strong class="text-on-surface">2 hours</strong> of placing the order at <a href="mailto:fullonbaan@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">fullonbaan@gmail.com</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">3. Refund Eligibility</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">Refunds may be considered under the following circumstances:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
          <li>You were charged but did not receive the product within 48 hours of confirmed payment</li>
          <li>You were charged more than once for the same order due to a technical error</li>
          <li>The product delivered is materially different from what was described on the product page</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">Refund requests must be submitted within <strong class="text-on-surface">7 days</strong> of the purchase date.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">4. Non-Refundable Cases</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">Refunds will <strong class="text-on-surface">not</strong> be provided in the following situations:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
          <li>The digital content has already been downloaded or accessed</li>
          <li>Change of mind after purchase</li>
          <li>Incompatibility with devices not meeting standard PDF/video requirements</li>
          <li>Partial use of combo or bundle products</li>
          <li>Requests made after 7 days of purchase</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">5. How to Request a Refund</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">To initiate a refund request, please email us at <a href="mailto:fullonbaan@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">fullonbaan@gmail.com</a> with the subject line <strong class="text-on-surface">"Refund Request — [Order Reference]"</strong> and include:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 ml-2">
          <li>Your full name and registered email address</li>
          <li>Payment reference / Razorpay transaction ID</li>
          <li>Reason for the refund request</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">We will review your request and respond within 3 business days.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">6. Refund Processing</h2>
        <p>Approved refunds will be processed to the original payment method within <strong class="text-on-surface">5–7 business days</strong> after approval. The timeline may vary depending on your bank or payment provider. GST amounts included in the original payment will be refunded in full if the refund is approved.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">7. Failed Payments</h2>
        <p>If your payment fails and your account is debited, the amount will be automatically reversed to your account within 5–7 business days by your bank or payment provider. If you do not receive the reversal, please contact us with your transaction details.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-xl text-on-surface mb-3">8. Contact</h2>
        <p>For cancellation or refund queries, contact us at <a href="mailto:fullonbaan@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">fullonbaan@gmail.com</a> or +91 63605 93122. You can also visit our <a href="/contact/" class="text-primary hover:underline">Contact page</a>.</p>
      </div>

